metadata.name: Nifty Sax x IMMUSE #001
metadata.title: Altair - AR
metadata.description: Altair - AR is soothing yet mysterious. Calming yet haunting. Just like outer space - which is exactly where IMMUSE set the scene for this Nifty Sax Visual Single. The AR scene features two celestial bodies orbiting each other, distorting the gravitational field, and emitting energy waves of light and sound. Saxtranauts tumble and drift about, as if ejected from the sax itself, a nod to Kubrickâ€™s, 2001: A Space Odyssey. Altair was originally released as 1 of 55 unique audio-reactive tokens in the Spheres Collection, dropped by Nifty Sax - an OG innovator in Web3 Music. The project minted and sold out in Sep 2021, paving the way for Web3 music. The original Spheres artwork has now been reimagined in AR as an audio reactive Milky Way galaxy. Remixable elements include Star One, Star Two, the Saxtronauts, and the Space Dust.
